Put this on a label (outside the gallery) to see exact field names:

Mid(JSON(First('kpi.vKPI_OnePagerUX')),1,1200)


Then edit the 3 ShowColumns(...,"ObjectivesText"/"PrioritiesText"/"KPIsText")
to match exactly.

If Step 1 fails: remove and re-add the data source so Power Apps refreshes the schema (Data pane â†’ â€¦ â†’ Remove â†’ Add data â†’ SQL â†’ Views â†’ pick kpi.vKPI_OnePagerUX).

